{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给罗石泉的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给罗石泉的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年8月23日）石泉兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到，甚以为慰，在地方上做些有益于人民的工作较为适宜，不必来京。此复，顺问康吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十三日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]罗石泉（1888—1951），湖南韶山市杨林乡杨林村人，乡村教师。毛泽东的原配罗氏的堂兄。1925年参加韶山农民运动，并加入中国共产党，曾任湖南湘潭（韶山）特别区农民协会执行委员、商民协会执行委员。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":23}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":102,"page_end":102},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}